Text: Final Reminder Please complete your online YPO Forum Diagnostic SurveyFinal Reminder Please complete your online YPO Forum Diagnostic Survey response today Bill Evans will be discussing your survey results with your forum when he meets with you October It is important that your forum has a response rate Go to Login Please ensure that your email and password are all lowercase and then click on the underlined word Login Password forum If you are the forum moderator you will use your MODERATOR password On the next page click on click here to complete your survey Upon completing your responses you will reach a confirmation page If you still have difficulty provide me with your fax number and Id be glad to fax the questionnaire to you Thank you Lisa Gaertner The Evans Group Quorum Drive Suite Dallas Texas fax
